Take US dollars dated post-2006. Most outlets and individuals will not accept or exchange older currency. Euros may also be exchanged. Thereâ€™s a shortage of foreign exchange currencies in Burundi.
Credit and debit cards are accepted in some places, (including Bon prix shops,Roca Golf, Kiriri Garden and Club du Lac and most of the major and modern hotels) but rarely outside Bujumbura. Mobile money is also often used in these hotels. ATMs are available, mainly in Bujumbura.
